October in the world of electronic music means only 1 thing - the Amsterdam Dance Event, a conference where everyone in the industry comes together in Amsterdam from agents to djs, managers, promoters, producers and labels!
 Perfecto Records proudly presents Amsterdam Dance Event 2014 a collection of current big tracks as well as some awesome exclusives from Perfecto artists.
 This years collection includes a dj mix as well as exclusive material from Magnus, Benjani, Shadow of Two and more! A real taste of what's coming up on Perfecto and Perfecto Fluoro!
